    <p>JON HUNTSMAN: We've got to wake up, when all is said and done, on Wednesday morning or Tuesday night and find that we have exceeded market expectations.</p>
    <p>ANDREA MITCHELL: You know, Romney is in such a commanding position, what about the expectations game...</p>
